<text top="550" left="157" width="81" height="17" font="11"><b>Acting </b></text>
<text top="550" left="208" width="248" height="17" font="11"><b>President</b>: I now invite the attention </text>
<text top="568" left="90" width="367" height="17" font="3">of the General Assembly to documents A/60/989 and </text>
<text top="586" left="90" width="367" height="17" font="3">A/60/992, circulated under agenda item 161, entitled </text>
<text top="604" left="90" width="366" height="17" font="3">"Extension of the term of the permanent judges of the </text>
