<text top="640" left="90" width="367" height="17" font="3">Persons Responsible for Genocide and Other Serious </text>
<text top="658" left="90" width="380" height="17" font="3">Violations of International Humanitarian Law </text>
<text top="676" left="90" width="367" height="17" font="3">Committed in the Territory of Rwanda and Rwandan </text>
